{"article_id":"4nfs5iB6IIiHKr4Z","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A president","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"who talks and acts tough on trade","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"has been a long time coming .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Donald Trump made getting fair dealing on trade a major plank in his campaign platform","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"and has followed through .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"China can ' t say","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"it wasn ' t warned about the imposition this week of additional tariffs on selected goods","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"coming into the United States .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Bad trade deals have cost the United States billions of dollars","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"and cost millions of American workers their jobs over the last several decades .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"Supporters of free trade find tariffs against China , Europe , Mexico and Canada hard to take .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Tariffs are taxes","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"hiding under another name","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"and lead to higher prices for U.S. consumers .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"The stock market dropped 500 points","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"after the new China tariffs were announced .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"Tariffs provide a safe harbor for inefficiencies ,","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"and protect markets and manufacturers from the need","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"to innovate","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"and increase productivity .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"But as a short-term strategy","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"to get the Chinese to the table","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"to make agreements","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"to protect American intellectual property , for example ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"it might be that rare occasion","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"on which to do something bad","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"so that good may come .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"A tariff strategy worked with the Europeans , and for Japan , Mexico and Canada ,","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"and now they ' re talking about new trade deals","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"that critics of the president said","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"would never happen .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Mr. Trump must remember","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"that a deal on paper and signed is only the beginning .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"Other signatories to a deal will be tempted to cheat","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"if they think","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"they can get away with it .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"This is what ' s happening now with Qatar ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"which","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"by being too clever by half","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"found a workaround to an agreement","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"it concluded with the United States","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"regarding the operation of the heavily subsidized Qatar Airways .","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"Under a deal","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"cut a year-and-a-half ago under Open Skies , an international regulatory regime","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"meant to enable open entry into a nation ' s airspace ,","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"an airline must not use government subsidies","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"to establish lower fares in competition with U.S. carriers .","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"Qatar , a nominal U.S. ally and host to the largest American military base in the Gulf , agreed to terms in January 2018","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"it is now subverting through its purchase of a 49 % share in an Italian carrier","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"it renamed Air Italy .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Soon afterward , Air Italy said","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"it would offer bargain-rate flights from Milan to New York , Miami , Los Angeles and San Francisco .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Qatar is using Air Italy","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"to get access to gates at U.S. airports","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"it said","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"it would not pursue under its own name .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"The word for that is cheating .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Qatar Airways is not being shy about it .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Air Italy is operating flights with Qatar Airways aircraft , with financing","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"provided by the Qatar government .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Its financial statements show","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Qatar Airways covers Air Italy ' s operating losses .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"Air Italy ' s chief operating officer and ranking executives are former Qatar Airways senior executives .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Air Italy crew uniforms","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"that are just like those","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"worn by Qatar Airways crews .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"This hasn ' t escaped the notice of U.S. carriers ,","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"which are rightly angry about it .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"American advocates on Capitol Hill ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"including Sen. Ted Cruz of Texas , a conservative Republican , and Bob Menendez of New Jersey , a liberal Democrat ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"are trying to do something about it .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"They ' re asking the Trump administration what it intends to do .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Unless pushed ,","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"probably nothing .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Qatar must be called to account , and not just for its own mischief","depth":4},{"id":75,"text":"but for the message","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"that would send to the Chinese and other major U.S. trading partners .","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"If Qatar Airways continues to use Air Italy as its proxy ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"and gets by with it ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"that would tell China , Japan , Mexico , Canada and Europe","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"they can agree to trade deals","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"and","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"if they ' re caught cheating","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"the United States will look the other way .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Someone could write a book ,","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"and call it \" The Art of the Steal . \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":171,"left":101,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":90,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":88,"right":89,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":88,"left":87,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":87,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":92,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":5,"right":91,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":91,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":93,"right":98,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":93,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":96,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":10,"right":95,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":94,"right":13,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":94,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":115,"right":169,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":104,"right":114,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":16,"right":103,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":17,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":114,"left":110,"right":113,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":107,"r